{"name":"http-promise","version":"0.1.4","description":"HTTP server based on Promises","main":"index.js","scripts":{"test":"node node_modules/mocha/bin/mocha test/spec","codeclimate":"node node_modules/codeclimate-test-reporter/bin/codeclimate.js < coverage.lcov"},"repository":"https://github.com/kwiniarski/http-promise","keywords":["http","server","promise"],"config":{"blanket":{"data-cover-only":"index.js","data-cover-never":"node_modules"}},"license":"MIT","dependencies":{"bluebird":"^3.1.1","chai":"^3.4.1","codeclimate-test-reporter":"^0.1.1","mocha-lcov-reporter":"^1.0.0","mocha-multi":"^0.7.2"},"devDependencies":{"blanket":"^1.1.6","chai":"^2.1.1","chai-http":"^1.0.0","codeclimate-test-reporter":"0.0.4","coffee-script":"^1.9.1","mocha":"^2.1.0","mocha-lcov-reporter":"0.0.2","mocha-multi":"^0.6.0"},"gitHead":"7e66eecfde64390ff59eed93c10c1307fe0c9174","homepage":"https://github.com/kwiniarski/http-promise#readme","versions":[{"number":"0.1.0","date":"2015-03-07T09:30:33.155Z"},{"number":"0.1.1","date":"2015-03-07T21:05:47.382Z"},{"number":"0.1.2","date":"2015-03-07T21:41:21.471Z"},{"number":"0.1.3","date":"2015-12-29T14:20:57.050Z"},{"number":"0.1.4","date":"2015-12-29T14:35:48.347Z"}],"readme":"# http-promise\n\nSimple module that adds promisified version of Node's `http.Server`.\n\n## Installation\n\n```\nnpm install http-promise --save-dev\n```\n\n## Usage\n\nTo use promisified server, just create it with `createServerAsync()`.\n\n```\nvar httpPromise = require('http-promise');\n\nhttpPromise.createServerAsync()\n  .listen(8000)\n  .tap(function (server) {\n         console.log(server.address());\n     })\n  .delay(5000)\n  .close()\n  .then(console.log)\n  .catch(console.error);\n```\n\n## API\n\nOnly two `http.Server` methods are promisified:\n\n* `listen`\n* `close`\n\nThose methods act as usual, expect they return a promise.\n\n\n","created":"2015-03-07T09:30:33.155Z","modified":"2015-12-29T14:35:48.347Z","lastPublisher":{"name":"kwiniarski","email":"krzysiek@codilogy.com"},"owners":[{"name":"kwiniarski","email":"contact@krzysztofwiniarski.com"}],"other":{"_attachments":{},"_from":".","_id":"http-promise","_nodeVersion":"4.1.1","_npmUser":{"name":"kwiniarski","email":"krzysiek@codilogy.com"},"_npmVersion":"2.14.4","_rev":"1-7ea0e73331727dad151b157a2c80ce0f","_shasum":"9c56ad7b2ff84d486031e9880de276b4d08ed650","author":{"name":"Krzysztof Winiarski"},"bugs":{"url":"https://github.com/kwiniarski/http-promise/issues"},"directories":{},"dist-tags":{"latest":"0.1.4"},"dist":{"shasum":"9c56ad7b2ff84d486031e9880de276b4d08ed650","tarball":"http://registry.npmjs.org/http-promise/-/http-promise-0.1.4.tgz"},"maintainers":[{"name":"kwiniarski","email":"contact@krzysztofwiniarski.com"}],"readmeFilename":"README.md","time":{"modified":"2015-12-29T14:35:48.347Z","created":"2015-03-07T09:30:33.155Z","0.1.0":"2015-03-07T09:30:33.155Z","0.1.1":"2015-03-07T21:05:47.382Z","0.1.2":"2015-03-07T21:41:21.471Z","0.1.3":"2015-12-29T14:20:57.050Z","0.1.4":"2015-12-29T14:35:48.347Z"}}}